Features:
    ☐ Install self; run on boot
    ☐ Install steamcmd
    ☐ Install VDS
    ☐ Update VDS
    ☐ List worlds
    ☐ Add/delete world
    ☐ Upload/download world data
    ☐ Start/stop world
    ☐ Persist configuration
    ☐ Password authentication
    ☐ Set backup frequency

API:
    ☐ sqlite
    ☐ Auth header
    ☐ GET /world (list worlds)
    ☐ POST /world (new world)
    ☐ PATCH /world (update world)
    ☐ GET /installs (get install status)
    ☐ POST /installs (do install / update)
    ☐ GET /status (resource usage, general status)

Server functions:
    ☐ Run install cmd
    ☐ Run update cmd
    ☐ Start world process (with guardian)
    ☐ Stop world process